IMAPAccount goods
Host mail.sbermegamarket.ru
User akselrod
PassCmd "gpg2 -q --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -d ~/.mbsyncpass-sbermegamarket.gpg"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt
AuthMechs LOGIN
SSLVersions TLSv1.2


IMAPStore goods-remote
Account goods

MaildirStore goods-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/.mail/goods/
Inbox ~/.mail/goods/Inbox

Channel goods
Far :goods-remote:
Near :goods-local:
# Exclude everything under the internal [Gmail] folder, except the interesting folders
#Patterns *Â ![Goods]* "[Goods]/Sent Mail" "[Goods]/Starred" "[Goods]/All Mail"
# Or include everything
#Patterns *
# Automatically create missing mailboxes, both locally and on the server
Create Both
# Sync the movement of messages between folders and deletions, add after making sure the sync works
Expunge Both
# Save the synchronization state files in the relevant directory
SyncState *